#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:86
msgid "QEMU"
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:88
msgid ""
"[QEMU](https://www.qemu.org/) is the most widely used open-source machine "
"emulator and virtualizer. It supports full system emulation as well as user-"
"mode binary translation."
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:90
msgid ""
"Asterinas does not yet support hardware-assisted virtualization (KVM), "
"therefore QEMU runs exclusively with **TCG** (Tiny Code Generator / software "
"emulation) on Asterinas NixOS."
msgstr ""

#: src/distro/popular-applications/containerization-and-virtualization/index.md:94
msgid ""
"```nix\n"
"environment.systemPackages = with pkgs; [ qemu_kvm ];\n"
"\n"
"environment.variables = {\n"
"  LINUX_BZIMAGE = \"${pkgs.linuxPackages.kernel}/bzImage\";\n"
"  OVMF_PATH = \"${pkgs.OVMF.fd}/FV/OVMF.fd\";\n"
"};\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

